refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraylstat stringfilename
获取由 filename 指定的文件或符号连接的统计信息。本函数和 stat 函数相同，只除了如果 filename 参数是符号连接的话，则该符号连接的状态被返回，而不是该符号连接所指向的文件的状态。
有关 lstat 返回的数组结构见手册中 stat 函数的页面。
&note.clearstatcache;
&tip.fopen-wrapper.stat;
参见 stat。

&reftitle.parameters;




   filename



     Path to a file or a symbolic link.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Comparison of stat and lstat


<?php
symlink('uploads.php', 'uploads');

// Contrast information for uploads.php and uploads
array_diff(stat('uploads'), lstat('uploads'));
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


     Information that differs between the two files.



Array
(
    [ino] => 97236376
    [mode] => 33188
    [size] => 34
    [atime] => 1223580003
    [mtime] => 1223581848
    [ctime] => 1223581848
    [blocks] => 8
)
